# DESCRIPTION

A simple stacking window manager with dynamic tiling capabilities.

 - Not as friendly as a full DE ;
 - Not as compliant with EWMH as lots existing WMs ;
 - Not as lean as a pure tiling WMs ;

But mixes floating and tiling modes smoothly with user
experience closest to usual.

# INSTALL

bash

[PREFIX=PATH] NDEBUG=1 [sudo] make install

tcsh

( setenv [PREFIX PATH] NDEBUG 1 ; [doas] make install )

# DOCUMENTATION

See stack(1) and stack.conf(5)

